# RunwayCtrl (public repo) — Environment Variables
#
# This public repository contains SDK/library scaffolding and contributor tooling.
# The proprietary control plane/runtime (and its configuration) is not published here.
#
# Most contributors will not need any environment variables to build, lint, or test.

# Optional: enable extra debug logging in local scripts/tools (if any are added later)
# LOG_LEVEL=debug
